Bootstrap: docker
From: pytorch/pytorch:2.5.1-cuda12.1-cudnn9-runtime

%post
    apt-get update -y && \
    apt-get install -y git libgl1 libglib2.0-0 && \
    apt-get clean && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

    # Placeholder dirs (masked by cluster /data bind at runtime; kept for convention).
    mkdir -p /data/BCI-AB /data/MIST-HER2

    pip install --no-cache-dir --upgrade pip

    # UGATIT uses cv2 (utils.py, UGATIT.py) and PIL (dataset.py).
    # scipy is a transitive dependency from the smoke-test environment.
    pip install --no-cache-dir \
        "opencv-python-headless==4.10.0.84" \
        "pillow==10.4.0" \
        "scipy==1.13.1"

%labels
    Author vsc21212
    Model UGATIT
    BaseImage pytorch/pytorch:2.5.1-cuda12.1-cudnn9-runtime
    PyTorch 2.5.1+cu121
    Python 3.11
    Benchmark InViLabVirtualStainingBenchmark

%help
    UGATIT (light) container for the InViLab virtual staining benchmark.
    Python 3.11, PyTorch 2.5.1 (cu121), CUDA 12.1 runtime.
    The cluster CUDA 12.x driver is backward compatible with this runtime.

    UGATIT hardcodes testA/testB folder names in build_model(). BCI-AB.sqsh
    and MIST-HER2.sqsh use valA/valB, so the HPC scripts bind valA and valB
    from the real archives into per-run testA and testB mount directories.

    Mount path convention:
      $VSC_SCRATCH/BCI-AB.sqsh trainA -> $VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit/BCI_full_i1M/trainA
      $VSC_SCRATCH/BCI-AB.sqsh valA   -> $VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit/BCI_full_i1M/testA
      $VSC_SCRATCH/MIST-HER2.sqsh valB -> $VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit/MIST-HER2_full_i1M/testB

    UGATIT args (BCI example):
      --dataroot $VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit   (parent of the dataset folder)
      --dataset  BCI_full_i1M

    Training (BCI, part 1 -- 500k iterations, no LR decay):
      srun apptainer exec --nv \
        -B $VSC_DATA:$VSC_DATA \
        -B $VSC_SCRATCH/BCI-AB.sqsh:$VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit/BCI_full_i1M/trainA:image-src=/trainA \
        -B $VSC_SCRATCH/BCI-AB.sqsh:$VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit/BCI_full_i1M/trainB:image-src=/trainB \
        -B $VSC_SCRATCH/BCI-AB.sqsh:$VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit/BCI_full_i1M/testA:image-src=/valA \
        -B $VSC_SCRATCH/BCI-AB.sqsh:$VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit/BCI_full_i1M/testB:image-src=/valB \
        $VSC_SCRATCH/containers/ugatit_nvidia.sif \
        python main.py \
          --dataset BCI_full_i1M --dataroot $VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit \
          --light True --img_size 512 --load_size 1024 \
          --iteration 500000 --decay_flag False ...

    Inference (BCI):
      srun apptainer exec --nv \
        -B $VSC_DATA:$VSC_DATA \
        -B $VSC_SCRATCH/BCI-AB.sqsh:$VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit/BCI_full_i1M/trainA:image-src=/trainA \
        -B $VSC_SCRATCH/BCI-AB.sqsh:$VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit/BCI_full_i1M/trainB:image-src=/trainB \
        -B $VSC_SCRATCH/BCI-AB.sqsh:$VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit/BCI_full_i1M/testA:image-src=/valA \
        -B $VSC_SCRATCH/BCI-AB.sqsh:$VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit/BCI_full_i1M/testB:image-src=/valB \
        $VSC_SCRATCH/containers/ugatit_nvidia.sif \
        python main.py \
          --phase test --dataset BCI_full_i1M --dataroot $VSC_SCRATCH/sqsh_mnt/ugatit \
          --light True --img_size 512 --load_size 1024 ...
